  <h2 class="p-tldr-logo"><a href="/tldr">TL;DR</a></h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <span class="date">March 10, 2016 </span>
      <h4><a data-analytics-link="tldr" class="chorus-optimize" data-chorus-optimize-id="10960429" data-chorus-optimize-module="*" data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" href="http://www.theverge.com/2016/3/10/11196388/virtual-reality-table-gif">Virtual reality desk claims another victim</a></h4>
      <span class="byline">By <a href="http://www.theverge.com/users/ctplante">Chris Plante</a></span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="date">March 10, 2016 </span>
